	# This file is part of the "More realistic traffic" mod for SCS ATS.
	#
	# This file contains color examples for various vehicle models and is intended
	# for inclusion in AI vehicle model files. The values given are originally from
	# the paintref web page.
	#
	# The distribution of the colors was based on the information on the edmunds web
	# page. To reflect the color distribution, some colors are listed here more than
	# once.
	#
	# - White colors:  ~25%  (6 colors, 250 times repeated)
	# - Gray colors:   ~21%  (11 colors, 115 times repeated)
	# - Black colors:  ~20%  (4 colors, 300 times repeated)
	# - Silver colors: ~11%  (5 colors, 132 times repeated)
	# - Blue colors:   ~10%  (23 colors, 26 times repeated)
	# - Red colors:    ~8%   (15 colors, 32 times repeated)
	# - Green colors:  ~1.8% (21 colors, 5 times repeated)
	# - Brown colors:  ~1.3% (10 colors, 8 times repeated)
	# - Orange colors: ~0.6% (9 colors, 4 times repeated)
	# - Yellow colors: ~0.2% (8 colors, 1 time repeated)
	# - Gold colors:   ~0.2% (1 color, 12 times repeated)
	# - Purple colors: ~0.1% (6 colors, 1 time repeated)
	# - Other colors:  ~0.8% (6 colors, 8 times repeated)

